The following energy sources are eligible renewable energy sources:
* hydro;
* wave;
* tide;
* ocean;
* wind;
* solar;
* geothermal-aquifer;
* hot dry rock;
* energy crops;
* wood waste;
* agricultural waste;
* waste from processing of agricultural products;
* food waste;
* food processing waste;
* bagasse;
* black liquor;
* biomass-based components of municipal solid waste;
* landfill gas;
* sewage gas and biomass-based components of sewage;
* any other energy source prescribed by the regulations.
* fossil fuels;
* materials or waste products derived from fossil fuels.

